{"id": 2726, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在职场中都碰到过哪些奇迹般的“走运时刻”？", "description": "职场马太效应，运气差的一路倒霉到头，运气好的机会越来越多，你是后边这种吗？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive ）", "record_count": 1181, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201901081206115rUMTwxXjhYyFlGf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-12T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 327170, "content": "我这属于一路坎坷，一入职就面临裁员的风险，整个部门人心惶惶，好不容易熬过去了，又听说下个季度更严重，每次吃饭看着大家不再看资讯，是在看工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582165}, {"id": 337928, "content": "问题解决了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 327180, "content": "第一份工作增进了自己的见识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560266}, {"id": 327181, "content": "遇到三观很对脾气的老板", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 327182, "content": "抢红包，运气最佳！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 327191, "content": "因为其他人分工明确术业有专攻，反而承接了各种别人不爱管的大项目一个人从头跑到尾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761046}, {"id": 329753, "content": "嘘～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 330013, "content": "我在等低运势的回马枪……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516110}, {"id": 328503, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799878}, {"id": 327230, "content": "逢考必过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 338497, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 327257, "content": "走运？做梦！不出大娄子就已经谢天谢地了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582627}, {"id": 328037, "content": "遇到一个好师傅愿意带着你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384343}, {"id": 328043, "content": "当拿到奖金的时候发现比预期高了很多很多，然而那时我已经离职跳去了竞争对手公司。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438893}, {"id": 328049, "content": "莫名其妙地开始做产品经理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586869}, {"id": 327547, "content": "羡慕你们。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3000}, {"id": 352644, "content": "\n走的是狗屎运！只是碰到狗屎，没有黄金！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665244}, {"id": 327300, "content": "被部门总监御姐看上，破格招入，给我想都没想过的薪资！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396310}, {"id": 327045, "content": "年会算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292442}, {"id": 327046, "content": "梦想去到超级难入的一个部门，在同事鼓励下去找领导自荐之后居然成功了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571404}, {"id": 327047, "content": "对明天的工作还有一些小期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931725}, {"id": 327048, "content": "做电话销售离职最后一天来了客户", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498827}, {"id": 327050, "content": "获得一位忘年交", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420463}, {"id": 327052, "content": "别家都裁员，我们逆势招人", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952931}, {"id": 327054, "content": "早上睡过，慌张出门的时候看到领导上午请假，吃个早餐再走吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270928}, {"id": 327566, "content": "提前没有注意到的冲突了的会议，一方客户临时请假，顺利过关😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583982}, {"id": 327055, "content": "没有实习 家里蹲一年 独自飞千里去广州投奔姬友养猫修门水管、闭关一个月 以为要和灰溜溜回家的时候拿到了offer 月薪4000包住！", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2337}, {"id": 327057, "content": "毕业后第一份到现在的工作team都和谐 老大人都很nice 让我保持在学院的单纯环境里度过五年 一直都工作开心 现在在做正义的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2337}, {"id": 327059, "content": "不喜欢做销售的我被老客户开发的新渠道带飞，不过毕竟不是长久之计吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 327061, "content": "莫名其妙的成为项目负责人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581430}, {"id": 327063, "content": "主管是个很会带下属的人，第一年就拿了最佳员工", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580548}, {"id": 327064, "content": "\n身处水深火热的我进来吃柠檬", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337324}, {"id": 327065, "content": ",找，咑，字，圆，简单好做，曰入11o~36o:微杏hy1️⃣2️⃣8️⃣9️⃣0️⃣0️⃣", "image": "img/option/option/20190212135851aRmEkwi3nGfNyTKq", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581470}, {"id": 327322, "content": "没换一个岗位都能获得部门boss的高度信任。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579485}, {"id": 327067, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 327323, "content": "每换一个岗位都能获得部门boss的高度信任。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579485}, {"id": 327328, "content": "干了坏事以后有人背锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429324}, {"id": 327076, "content": "多动动，总有好处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577288}, {"id": 327077, "content": "头天开年会第二天部门被裁", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489010}, {"id": 327078, "content": "选学生会文艺部长，三个人，我全票过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577896}, {"id": 327079, "content": "并没有，大概我没有点幸运天赋吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496704}, {"id": 327081, "content": "没有好运气过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549166}, {"id": 327082, "content": "年会中iPhone", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581606}, {"id": 327083, "content": "诅咒你们这些走运的，哼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 327085, "content": "希望今年有好运！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581624}, {"id": 327093, "content": "从来就没有走运过。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508609}, {"id": 327094, "content": "离职前一周得知公司绩效不好发不出工资了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643054}, {"id": 327095, "content": "只有奇迹般的倒霉时刻\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468606}, {"id": 327098, "content": "陪同学去校招 被希尔顿老板看中 可以免试上岗 可惜考上博了没去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581661}, {"id": 327102, "content": "清清浅浅", "image": "img/option/option/20190212173406YMJhmQj73VwbONKX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581430}]}